      "message": "Note: this sets the minimum interval between a roll CL landing and the next one being uploaded.  Because of CQ latency, the actual time at which the CL is uploaded could drift.  We also support a roll window, which can be used to ensure that rolls are only uploaded, eg. during working hours Mon-Fri, during the night, or whatever.  The roll window can be combined with maxRollFrequency to ensure that only one roll is uploaded per day but also ensure that it occurs within a specified window.",
